reviews.text: I have visited Str8 Out The Kitchen many times. I always order one of the many fish dinners, this visit the fish was salty & the greens was dry. They seemed...
Today was my first time trying it out because someone recommended it to me. Always drove past but never really sure if they were open or what to try. Today...
Great Turkey ribs, candied yams but those greens were WWWAAAYYYYY to salty. Can't do those again.
